{"id":4575,"date":"2022-08-26T06:18:15","date_gmt":"2022-08-26T06:18:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/kjoumaa.com\/klima\/?post_type=dt_portfolio&#038;p=4575"},"modified":"2024-12-23T09:22:49","modified_gmt":"2024-12-23T09:22:49","slug":"fire-damper","status":"publish","type":"dt_portfolio","link":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/products\/fire-damper\/","title":{"rendered":"Fire Damper"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;4864&#8243; img_size=&#8221;450&#215;350&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><u>Description<\/u><\/strong>:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Fire Damper is designed with the concept of the safety of human life and property. The challenging demand is the most crucial of all faced by building planners, fire damper protects individual rooms or zones by sealing off any supply or extract air, thus preventing the spread of fire through the central HVAC system of the building or the walls. It is designed to be in HVAC Duct system that passes through for resistant walls, partitions and air transfer opening in walls.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The frame is made from 1.2mm \u2013 1.6mm thick galvanized steel construction. All welded joints are rust proofed Zinc Paint Coating. The blades are roll formed 0.8 mm -1.0 mm thick galvanized steel. The interlocking type blades are designed with the shaped reinforcement ridged ensuring strength and stability. The blade ramp is formed 1.6 thick galvanized steel with springs firmly secured to the frame by rivets. The blades are secured by UL listed fusible links which have a fire rating of 165F-212F and thus kept out of the airflow when not in operation.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><u>Tests and Certification:<\/u><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The fire dampers are tested by UL laboratories and are manufactured in compliance with the <strong><u>UL555 standards<\/u><\/strong>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The heat responsive links (fusible link) on detection of heat beyond 165F\/212F release blades from their position. These fire dampers are rated up to 3 hours rating with low leakage.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">All Fire Dampers are manufactured in compliance with <strong><u>UL 555<\/u> <\/strong>standards and<strong><u> NFPA 90A<\/u><\/strong><\/span>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;4864&#8243; img_size=&#8221;450&#215;350&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text] Description: Fire Damper is designed with the concept of the safety of human life and property. The challenging demand is the most crucial of all faced by building planners, fire damper protects individual rooms or zones by sealing off any supply or extract air, thus preventing the spread of fire&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4864,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","dt_portfolio_category":[117],"dt_portfolio_tags":[],"class_list":["post-4575","dt_portfolio","type-dt_portfolio","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","dt_portfolio_category-ul-fire-protection","dt_portfolio_category-117","description-off"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_portfolio\/4575","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_portfolio"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/dt_portfolio"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/klimacontra.c